Class ValidatingCellEditor

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleEditor, IntegerEditor

    public abstract class ValidatingCellEditor
extends javax.swing.DefaultCellEditor
    Base class for creating table cell editors which have the capability to validate their contents. Logic for validation is my own.
    Author:
    Kevin J. Burns

      • performValidation

        protected abstract boolean performValidation(java.lang.Object v)
        This function is called when it is necessary to validate a table cell.
        Parameters:
